#!name = 外星仔助手(本地版)
#!desc = 解决脚本下载失败问题，包含视频倍速与广告拦截。

[Rule]
# 拦截已知的广告配置域名
DOMAIN, app-analytics-services.com, REJECT
DOMAIN, webcast-open.douyin.com, REJECT

[Script]
# 直接运行本地脚本逻辑，跳过远程下载
http-response ^https?:\/\/.*\.video\..*\/ script-path=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/NobyDa/Script/master/Loon/VideoPace.js, requires-body=true, timeout=10, tag=外星仔倍速

[MITM]
hostname = %APPEND% *.video.*, *.pangle.io, *.snssdk.com, webcast-open.douyin.com, app-analytics-services.com
